snippet.title: Official Aftermath Open Beta Trailer!
snippet.description: This is the official trailer for Romero's Aftermath Open Beta!  Check out more information at http://www.WillYouSurvive.com  Aftermath is a Free to Win zombie survival sandbox game!  Like, follow and tell your friends!  See you in game!
